Sally Wheeler https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sally_Wheeler 0 Sally Wheeler, (born May 19, 1970 in Winter Haven, Florida), is an American television actress, probably best known for her role in short-running series Two of a Kind alongside Mary-Kate and Ashley Olsen. Wheeler was a 1985 graduate of Winter Haven High School and received a Master of Fine Arts in acting from the University of Florida Sally_Wheeler , ( born May_19_,_1970 in Winter_Haven , Florida ) , is an_American_television_actress , probably best_known for her_role in short-running_series_Two of a_Kind alongside Mary-Kate and Ashley_Olsen .
